## üìù Typography (Text Sizes)

### Section Titles (H2)
```
text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black
```
| Device | Size | Approx px |
|--------|------|-----------|
| Mobile | `text-2xl` | 24px |
| Small | `sm:text-3xl` | 30px |
| Medium | `md:text-4xl` | 36px |

### Hero Title (H1)
```
text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black
```
| Device | Size | Approx px |
|--------|------|-----------|
| Mobile | `text-xl` | 20px |
| Small | `sm:text-2xl` | 24px |
| Medium | `md:text-3xl` | 30px |
| Large | `lg:text-4xl` | 36px |

### Card Title (H3)
- Standard: `text-sm font-bold` ‚Üí **14px**
- Featured: `text-sm sm:text-base font-bold` ‚Üí **14-16px**
- Gallery Featured: `text-sm sm:text-base font-bold` ‚Üí **14-16px**
- News Featured: `text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold` ‚Üí **18-24px**

### Description Text
- Hero: `text-xs sm:text-sm` ‚Üí **12-14px**
- Section: `text-sm` ‚Üí **14px**
- Card: `text-xs` / `text-[11px]` ‚Üí **11-12px**

### Micro Text (Badges, Labels, Meta)
- Badge: `text-[10px]` / `text-[11px]` ‚Üí **10-11px**
- Feature Highlight: `text-[9px]` ‚Üí **9px**
- Location: `text-[10px]` ‚Üí **10px**
- Stats Label: `text-[10px] uppercase` ‚Üí **10px**

### Stats Numbers
- Hero Stats: `text-lg sm:text-xl font-black` ‚Üí **18-20px**
- VideoInfo Stats: `text-xl sm:text-2xl font-black` ‚Üí **20-24px**

