## üìä Comparison: Home vs Destinations

| Element | Home | Destinations | Recommendation |
|---------|------|--------------|----------------|
| **Section Title** | `text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl` | `text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl` | Use Home sizing |
| **Card Title** | `text-sm font-bold` | `text-xl font-bold` | Reduce to `text-sm` |
| **Card Description** | `text-[11px]` | `text-sm` | Reduce to `text-[11px]` |
| **Badge Text** | `text-[10px]` | `text-xs` | Reduce to `text-[10px]` |
| **Card Width** | `w-[280px] sm:w-[320px]` | `w-80 (320px)` | Similar, OK |
| **Card Height** | Fixed `h-[350px]` | Auto | Consider fixed height |
| **Button Text** | `text-xs` | `text-sm font-semibold` | Reduce to `text-xs` |
| **Icon Size** | `w-3 h-3` / `w-4 h-4` | `w-5 h-5` / `w-6 h-6` | Reduce icons |
| **Meta Text** | `text-[10px]` | `text-sm` | Reduce to `text-[10px]` |
| **Section Padding** | `py-16 md:py-20` | `py-16 md:py-20` | Same, OK |

