## üîß Quick Fixes untuk Halaman Destinations

### 1. Hero Section
```diff
- text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black
+ text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black

- text-lg md:text-xl
+ text-xs sm:text-sm
```

### 2. Destination Card
```diff
- text-xl font-bold
+ text-sm font-bold

- text-sm line-clamp-2
+ text-[11px] line-clamp-6

- text-lg font-black (price)
+ text-sm font-bold (price)

- w-5 h-5 / w-6 h-6 (icons)
+ w-3 h-3 / w-4 h-4 (icons)
```

### 3. Filter Section
```diff
- text-sm font-medium
+ text-[11px] font-medium

- px-4 py-2 (category buttons)
+ px-3 py-1.5 (category buttons)
```

### 4. CTA Buttons
```diff
- px-5 py-2.5 ... text-sm
+ px-5 py-2.5 ... text-xs

- px-6 py-3 ... text-sm (mobile CTA)
+ px-5 py-2.5 ... text-xs (mobile CTA)
```

